*'''Master Spy''': [[File:Cap2 2998.jpg|thumb|250px|Sitwell leads the manhunt on [[Steve Rogers]]]] Sitwell was a master spy, making all of [[S.H.I.E.L.D.]] believe he was a loyal agent of theirs when in reality he was an operative of [[Hydra]]. According to his S.H.I.E.L.D. file, Sitwell worked primarily on Fury's most discreet and top-secret missions, having proven time and again that he was one of the agency's most dedicated and capable agents.
*'''Expert Investigator''': According to his S.H.I.E.L.D. file, Sitwell as an exceptional crime scene investigator. He tracked Benjamin Pollack and [[Claire Weiss]] to a hotel in south [[Florida]] after studying their many robberies.
*'''Martial Artist''': Sitwell had knowledge of hand-to-hand combat, easily overpowering [[Benjamin Pollack]] in a fight, though Pollack is not trained in combat.

==Equipment==
===Weapons===
*'''[[Scepter]]''': After the [[Battle of New York]], Sitwell and the [[STRIKE]] team retrieved the Scepter from the [[Avengers]], who had no suspicion.
*'''[[Chitauri Gun]]''': There were 47 [[Chitauri]] weapons after the [[Battle of New York]], only one of them was active, which was turned on by [[Benjamin Pollack]] and used to rob banks with his [[Claire Weiss|partner]]. Sitwell stopped them.

===Vehicles===
*'''[[Helicarrier]]''': Sitwell was stationed on the Helicarrier prior to the [[Battle of New York]].
*'''''[[Bus]]''''': During the [[Search for the Clairvoyant]], Sitwell and other agents discussed plans on the ''Bus''.
*'''''[[Lemurian Star]]''''': Sitwell was stationed on the Lemurian Star when it was hijacked by [[Georges Batroc]].

==Facilities==
*'''[[HYDRA Preparatory Academy]]''': Sitwell went to school at the secret academy to learn how to infiltrate [[S.H.I.E.L.D.]]
*'''[[S.H.I.E.L.D. Crater Investigation Site]]''': Sitwell was stationed in [[Puente Antiguo]], [[New Mexico]] to investigate an [[Mjølnir|0-8-4]]. He witnessed [[Thor]]'s attempt to get the item.
*'''[[Hub (S.H.I.E.L.D. Facility)|Hub]]''': Sitwell was at the Hub when [[Grant Ward]] and [[Leo Fitz]] were sent on a mission. He caught [[Jemma Simmons]] doing suspicious activities and wound up getting sedated by Simmons.
*'''[[Triskelion]]''': Sitwell was at the Triskelion during the [[Hydra Uprising]] and was actively involved in searching for [[Steve Rogers|Captain America]].

